...If you wish to speak, then speak. I

...Oh, them. You haven't wiped them

39:

44:

47:
Listening to the excuses of sinners is

guilty is just.
49:
Preventing them from staining

54:
...Punishment is necessary, but I

of a second chance. They will need

59: ...Hah. What a big heart you have.
62:
...In that case, why not request aid

64:
After all, he is both a mighty king
and a great hero. He doubtless has
a capacity for mercy that I cannot
match. Perhaps they will listen to

70:
If that's what you're getting at, why
don't you let me tell you a thing or
two about my bro Nimbus?
80:
Bro was swept away to another
world when he was just a kid and
was treated like a slave growing up.
84:
Spare me your drivel! That man is a
Whitetail, is he not? Such a thing is
impossible!
88:
His whole world was nothing but
sand in every direction. No dogfolk

91:
I don't know how that compares to
the circumstances you've faced as
a lionfolk, but I think a little mutual
understanding's not out of the
question.
99:
...This doesn't have anything to do
with Whitetail. We just need you to
talk to them.
103:
We're heading out tomorrow
morning. Be ready to go by then.
110:
We're leaving the rest to you. All
right?
114:
...I'll give it a try, but don't get your
hopes up too much.
117:
I-is that Magnos? That's impossible!
You're supposed to be dead!
126:
None of you are free of sin, but
surrender now and your lives will be
spared.
129:
...I do not wish to needlessly shed
blood, either. Acknowledge your sins
and accept your faults. If you doâ€”
134:
We've just been following your
orders! Kill, steal, burn to the ground!
No one ever told us to stop!
135:
And you! You said you'd change the
world, and then we'd...
Wait, sin? We're sinners, did you say?
137:
I see... You're one of "them" now,
aren't you, Magnos?
140: N-no... I merely... I merely came toâ€”
143:
You merely what? Please, enlighten
us, great Magnos!
145:
Who do we need to kill this time to
find salvation?!
159:
...Sorry, but this has gone far enough.
All troops, prepare to charge.
168:
We're the same! They're just
enragedâ€”
177:
Sheesh, wish you would've spoken

181:
Everything's gonna be okay. It's all
going according to plan.
192:
They said there weren't any
casualties in today's fight.
196:
You came all the way here to tell me
that?
200:
I thought it might be bothering you.
Claw said you looked really upset.
204:
...It was supposed to be an act of
atonement.
206:
Their existence is another of my
many sins, so I thought it would be

210: But you wanted to help them.
216:
That cry of rage... I know it all too

220:
...Yup. You've got a little kindness in

224:
...Shut up. I am not the same as the
rest of you.
228:
Yeah, I know. If you were like the rest

happening.
236:
Nimbus probably wouldn't suddenly
bring up someone's age just
because they talked back to him.
245:
But I know you're a kind person. Even

249:
I've been shaking that sort of thing

253:
Then why don't you just try asking

256:
If you keep everything all bottled up,
it's gonna affect you in a bad way

264:
...No, you're right. It's exactly as you

267:
...Hey, Teo. Would you mind
discussing this with me further?
